    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.02093.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline> 
                    <name type="place">Adel Grange.<ptr target="loc.02093_n1"/></name>
                    <name type="place">Leeds.</name>
                    <name type="place">England.</name>
                    <date when="1888-12-30">30 Dec: 1888.</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Mr. Whitman</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Edward Carpenter<ptr target="n0141b"/> sent us on a letter he had received from
                you&#8212;in which you ask him for our address. Here it is at the
                top.</p>
            <p>Thank you very much <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.02093.002_large.jpg" type="verso"
                /> for remembering Bessie &amp; me.  We never never forget
                you&#8212;nor the great great debt we owe you for all you have written. We
                shall like to have an "Autumn
                    Boughs"<ptr target="n3999"/> very much&#8212;it is good of you to think of sending us
                one. I wish you were feeling better &amp; stronger.</p>
            <p>A friend of <choice><sic>your's</sic><corr>yours</corr></choice> saw you <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.02093.003_large.jpg"
                    type="recto"/> lately in America&#8212;&amp; wrote to us about his visit to
                you.</p>
            <p>Goodbye. Both Bessie &amp; I send you our warmest greetings for the New Year &amp;
                for all times.</p>
            <p>Your friends,</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Bessie &amp; Isabella Ford</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.02093.004_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            <pb xml:id="leaf003r" facs="loc.02093.005_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <note type="editorial" resp="#ww">Bessie &amp; Isabella Ford</note>
            <pb xml:id="leaf003v" facs="loc.02093.006_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
